_sText:
This is a construction-site-themed map where the terrorists start at the top and the counter-terrorists start at the bottom. The objective for the counter-terrorists is to save four hostages at the top of the building. The terrorists have to defend the building and kill all intruders. 

I'm still kinda new to making maps and this is actually one of the first that I've finished. 
Cons and pros will be appreciated.
